caption:
I sat down at this state’s capital building. Saw a monument to Volunteer Firemen in front of me. Then I wrote this.

Still head back to New York, but might not make it call at once. If not right to NY, I wonder where I should visit and have a loop around at.

As the water learns its place. [210617 0806]
